Product Description


Features:

1. New and in a good condition.
2. Made of durable and reliable material, harmless to your health.
3. It is easy to use, convenient to carry with.
4. The best replacement for the old or damaged one.
5. A great assistant for electric tools.
6. Provide convenience to charge your electric tool anytime and anywhere.
7. It is suitable for Makita BL1815, BL1830, BL1835, LXT400, 194204-5, 194205-3, 194309-1.

